iaik.pdf.asn1objects

Class RevocationInfoArchival

  • java.lang.Object
    • iaik.asn1.structures.AttributeValue
      • iaik.pdf.asn1objects.RevocationInfoArchival
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    iaik.asn1.ASN1Type

    public class RevocationInfoArchival
extends iaik.asn1.structures.AttributeValue
    This class represents the ASN.1 structure RevocationInfoArchival as defined in PDF specification ISO 32000-1: 
     RevocationInfoArchival ::= SEQUENCE {
                crl [0] EXPLICIT SEQUENCE of CRLs, OPTIONAL
                ocsp [1] EXPLICIT SEQUENCE of OCSP Responses, OPTIONAL
                otherRevInfo [2] EXPLICIT SEQUENCE of OtherRevInfo, OPTIONAL
 }
